    <title>Metric Template Guide</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Detailed guide for using and extending <ref refid="classmetric__template" kindref="compound">metric_template</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="metric_template_page_1metric_template_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <ref refid="classmetric__template" kindref="compound">metric_template</ref> class defines performance metrics for evaluating model performance and analysis results.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="metric_template_page_1metric_template_types">
<title>Metric Types</title>
<para>Common metrics include:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Classification: Accuracy, precision, recall, F1</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Regression: MSE, MAE, R²</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Physics-specific: Mass resolution, efficiency</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="metric_template_page_1metric_template_example">
<title>Example</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">AccuracyMetric<sp/>:<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classmetric__template" kindref="compound">metric_template</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>AccuracyMetric()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref><sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;accuracy&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>compute(<ref refid="structgraph__t" kindref="compound">graph_t</ref>*<sp/>data,<sp/>torch::Tensor<sp/>prediction)</highlight><highlight class="keyword"><sp/>override<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>truth<sp/>=<sp/>*data-&gt;<ref refid="structgraph__t_1acfe6c582dfe47bafa5cde3f4d87059a0" kindref="member">get_truth_node</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;label&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">this</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>pred_class<sp/>=<sp/>(prediction<sp/>&gt;<sp/>0.5).to(torch::kInt);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>correct<sp/>=<sp/>(pred_class<sp/>==<sp/>truth).<ref refid="classtools_1a7b784121d8b368a64995feddc7083469" kindref="member">sum</ref>().item&lt;</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal">&gt;();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>total<sp/>=<sp/>truth.size(0);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>accuracy<sp/>=<sp/>(float)correct<sp/>/<sp/>total;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">float</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>accuracy;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</sect1>
